<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="115" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,1063,1485]" pageId="7" pageNumber="115">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1351,1376]" pageId="7" pageNumber="115">Remarks.</emphasis>
The species was described from the mainland 
<collectingCountry box="[833,904,1351,1376]" name="China" pageId="7" pageNumber="115">China</collectingCountry>
. Recently, a new subspecpecies, 
<taxonomicName box="[1268,1428,1352,1376]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lesteva" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="115" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" subSpecies="taiwanica">
<emphasis box="[1268,1428,1352,1376]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="115">L. r. taiwanica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, was described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Shavrin" box="[353,522,1388,1413]" pageId="7" pageNumber="115" refString="Shavrin, A. V. (2015) New species and subspecies of the genus Lesteva Latreille, 1797 (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Omaliinae) from Taiwan. Zootaxa, 4032 (3), 333 - 338." type="journal article" year="2015">Shavrin (2015)</bibRefCitation>
from 
<collectingCountry box="[592,678,1388,1413]" name="Taiwan" pageId="7" pageNumber="115">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
. I provide here figures of the aedeagus (Figs. 19–20) more detailed than in 
<bibRefCitation author="Rougemont" box="[235,450,1424,1448]" pageId="7" pageNumber="115" refString="Rougemont, G. - M. de (2000) New species of Lesteva Latreille, 1796 from China (Insecta: Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). Annalen des Naturhistorischen Museums in Wien, 102 (B), 147 - 169." type="journal article" year="2000">Rougemont (2000)</bibRefCitation>
. The distribution as in 
<figureCitation box="[707,789,1423,1448]" captionStart="FIGURE 27" captionStartId="10.[151,250,1831,1853]" captionTargetBox="[182,1404,944,1810]" captionTargetId="figure@10.[182,1404,944,1810]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURE 27. Distribution of Lesteva rufopunctata rufopunctata Rougemont, 2000, south-western China." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/843149/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="115">Fig. 27</figureCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,1063,1485]" box="[199,731,1460,1485]" pageId="7" pageNumber="115">It is recorded here for Yunnan for the first time.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
